snippet.title: DIG VR | META QUEST RELEASE DATE TRAILER
snippet.description:
Our fun, authentic and immersive light-simulation excavator game will have you digging for more as it launches on MetaQuest VR on October the 24th!

Life is built for moments, and players will soon get the opportunity to create their own as they step into the virtual world of earth excavation. Featuring an easy to learn, but fun to master, realistic control scheme!

Use a variety of toolheads and customise your digger as you complete a variety of tasks in single and multiplayer scenarios and build moments of your own.

Wishlist: https://Wired.gg/DigVR
Sign up for more information: https://www.digvrgame.com 

#DIGVR
